name: RANGDA
description:
Queen of the leaks in Balinese myth. Rangda Bali resembles a scary creature which according to myth likes to kidnap small children and eat them. Rangda led an army of leak which is the power of evil against Barong which is a symbol of the power of good.

Illustrated as the Queen of Evil who is preparing food for her dinner near the temple
Place of offering The followers of Evil magic power
